    <p><h2>Donations</h2></p>
    <p>We use donations for helping development of Enlightenment, EFL
    or otherwise promoting it and the community. We will do our best to
    ensure that the money will always be used for a good cause and is
    not  mishandled in any way.</p>
    <p>We have set up a non-profit organization located in France to
    manage donations and other matters where we require a real entity to
    perform actions. It is this entity that manages the donated funds.
    For more information on this organization, please see
    <a href=http://enlightenment.fr/lassociation-enlightenment-francophone/>
    L’association Enlightenment Francophone</a>. The french information on
    how to donate is <a href=http://enlightenment.fr/dons/>Here</a>.
    </p>
   </div>
  </td>
   
